title: Season 5 Ranked Music - Piano Cover

embed.description: Here is a piano cover of the League of Legends ranked champion select music that came out in 2015, to go with the Summoner's Rift visual update. It has been replaced with new ranked music in the Season 6 champion select, but this music still lives on in featured and custom game modes.

body:
Here is a piano cover of the League of Legends ranked champion select music that came out in 2015, to go with the Summoner's Rift visual update. It has been replaced with new ranked music in the Season 6 champion select, but this music still lives on in featured and custom game modes.

I've seen a lot of videos covering the original champion select music in ranked (Seasons 1-4), but very few if at all covering the Season 5 one, so I thought I might do one. Plus it's still an epic piece of music and I am fairly happy with the result.

Enjoy!

Also, Zedd Ignite Piano Cover coming very soon.

replies.body: So good, hope to see many more creators and artists popping up.
